{"tid":1790871,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先等巴士俾疑似藍曱甴打尖上車","createTime":"2019-12-20T10:17:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T15:26:11.000Z","uid":281492,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2d6a07d7ca374572aaec66f5260453d797fb32","tid":1790871,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:17:26.000Z","msg":"頭先收工 black block等巴士<br />\n有個阿嬸排我後面<br />\n但係因為我哋個個都係面向對面馬路咁排<br />\n所以我見到佢眼超超咁望住我<br />\n可能見我全黑啦 我就冇理到佢<br />\n<br />\n架巴士嚟嗰陣<br />\n佢用力bell開我打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我用一個嫌棄佢嘅語氣講咗句：做咩事呀<br />\n佢頭也不回咁繼續嘟八達通<br />\n點知嘟唔到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺度摷摷摷又霸住唔俾人嘟咁<br />\n我即刻衝上前打返佢尖嘟卡<br />\n個阿嬸呆撚咗跟住好嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住我頭也不回咁上上層<br />\n隻老嘢應該關節酸痛所以跟唔到上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">係呀我仲用緊八達通<br />\n因為想攞政府個津貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"e287868bf158ac889a54ef126972f8fdce99b1be","tid":1790871,"uid":1891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T10:17:47.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ccF7Pwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FccF7Pwj.jpg&h=a4c97012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XcqBbk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XcqBbk.png&h=b08a4737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai